document_data.History:
When his older brother came to power in [[123 DR]], Amahl IV was appointed Caleph of [[Calimshan]]. He lusted after power and desired his elder brother's position, so he murdered him one day during a feast in Shoon III's harem in [[130 DR]] and took the crown.
