Every year, the ''qysar'' demanded that fireworks be loosed in his honor on his birthday. On one such occasion&mdash;fittingly, the [[138 DR|Year of Sparks Flying, 138 DR]]&mdash;several fires erupted in the poorer sections of [[Almraiven]], [[Calimport]], [[Memnon]], and [[Shoonach]]. Amahl blamed the Ilmatari, boldly claiming that they started the fires that killed thousands to ease their suffering.

After traveling for fifteen years, Amahl IV's brother, also named Amahl, returned in [[142 DR]] to find one brother mad and the other brother murdered. Amahl V tried to depose Amahl IV civilly, but Amahl IV refused to listen to reason and attempted to slay Amahl V with his magical scimitar. Amahl V, who was a [[wizard]], used a wind spell to blow his brother off the [[Imperial Mount]], where he fell to his death in the River Agis.

Amahl IV was buried at [[Nykkar]].
